org.springframework.cloud.sleuth.instrument.messaging

Class TraceMessageHeaders

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.cloud.sleuth.instrument.messaging.TraceMessageHeaders

  • public class TraceMessageHeaders
extends Object
    Contains trace related messaging headers. The deprecated headers contained `-` which for example in the JMS specs is invalid. That's why the public constants in this class represent the valid names for the tracing headers.
    Since:
    1.0.4
    Author:
    Marcin Grzejszczak
